high_descs: Go to the left and turn to the right to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and pick up the potato from the shelf.
Go left and then left again and turn to the right to face the sink.
Put the potato in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the potato up again.
Go left and walk forward to stand in front of the microwave.
Put the potato in the microwave and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean potato in the microwave.

high_descs: Pick up a potato from the fridge
Wash the potato in the sink
Place the potato in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Place a washed potato in a microwave

high_descs: Turn left and take one step, then turn right and take two steps, then turn right and face the fridge.
Open the fridge and take the potato that is on the shelf.
Turn left and walk to the counter, then turn left and take three steps, then turn right and face the sink.
Put the potato in the center of the sink, in between the tomato and apple, then turn on the faucet and let the water run for three seconds, then turn the sink off and take the potato.
Turn left and walk across the room.
Open the microwave and put the potato inside the microwave.
